title: Simple Text Editor in Python
subtitle: Made with Tkinter in Python
tags: [tkinter]
---

I wrote a simple text editor in python using the Tkinter graphical user interface library. It has two options: Save and Open which lets you open a .txt file within the simplistic text editor. However, you can save the file in whichever you format you wish.

Here are some working screenshots of this lightning fast text editor:

